{"tid":540715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魔術師大衛高柏飛被控迷姦少女","createTime":"2018-01-25T17:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T19:43:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"85a22b80e8d7ebf32934ac8f65e74ca90fa9237c","tid":540715,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"魔術師大衛考柏菲　 <br />\n被控迷姦未成年女模 <br />\n<br />\n出版時間：2018/01/25 18:29 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180125/640_a5180265e1eed4a6fd0fb687f20bba49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180125%2F640_a5180265e1eed4a6fd0fb687f20bba49.jpg&h=70729ff0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n知名魔術師大衛考柏菲德曾表演許多經典魔術。達志 <br />\n<br />\n現年61歲的美國知名魔術師大衛考柏菲（David Copperfield）在80、90年代紅極一時，他曾讓自由女神消失、飛越萬里長城的魔術表演，至今仍讓人津津樂道。但一名前模特兒布蘭妮路易斯（Brittney Lewis）出面控訴，80年代她仍是少女模特兒時，曾在加州一間旅館內遭他下藥性侵，但他矢口否認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控訴遭考柏菲迷姦的女模，現在已是40多歲的熟女，她向The Wrap網站表示，2人於1988年9月在日本結識，當時考柏菲擔任當地模特兒比賽的評審，她是其中一名參賽者，2人交換電話號碼，考柏菲還出錢讓她飛到加州，並讓她住在相連的飯店房間，她指出2人先在酒吧小酌，一度察覺他可能在飲料內下藥，「他當時辯稱只是在分飲料」，接著回到房間後「我記得我的衣服被脫去，他親我的臉，然後他開始親吻我的身體，接著當他開始親吻我的下半身，我完全失去意識」。 <br />\n<br />\n控訴者表示猶仍記得他隔天的態度，「他堅稱什麼事都沒發生，因為我當時未成年」，還逼她寫下聲明表示她沒事。她曾試著在2007年出面控訴，但她表示當時沒受到太多注意。 <br />\n<br />\n考柏菲則在個人推特表示，「多年來有許多關於我的不實指控與傳言報導，卻很少有媒體報導我的清白與這些控訴者被逮捕的事實，所以當我正面臨另外一個風暴，我希望#MeToo運動能持續發酵」，他呼籲大家不該急於將別人定罪。 <br />\n<br />\n（李子凡／綜合報導） <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180125/1285749/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180125%2F1285749%2F&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bw7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=05329df7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180125%2F1285749%2F&h=4dca9906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180125/1285749/</a>"},{"pid":"e3959604b85ebdb6d0e66aaeea4032f06c6f86a5","tid":540715,"uid":12021,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0080c906b28085cdd9f391b71580b143afbc58b","tid":540715,"uid":144466,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#METOO</blockquote><br />\n#METOO"},{"pid":"38f124e7758828226d43de6f0fd064288ba733e0","tid":540715,"uid":34562,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"變走你塊閪"},{"pid":"29dd370cf3c9ce3285e5a25911772f77a10b9281","tid":540715,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"一定係幻覺"},{"pid":"04f39ac71d9e244fac296366807f66c6e0e56585","tid":540715,"uid":105552,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:00:30.000Z","msg":"其實點解metoo完有班女人會跑出黎俾人性侵?<br />\n依個仲有30姆年前"},{"pid":"89a19a96c0b3584e57fc3fc60cd34f0513f6f94b","tid":540715,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:03:36.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"e37b5e2b955a6e6ea4c2421820daa812033b2ae5","tid":540715,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6abad6238c06681746727a49c536eef3e1728624","tid":540715,"uid":3668,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:05:15.000Z","msg":"#metoo=#need$"},{"pid":"d336895fd87ab112f8094170ad16a597cf30e8b0","tid":540715,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b85c2c3afe449ae11f174f35c0f8126d4eab5ddf","tid":540715,"uid":152123,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"d336895fd87ab112f8094170ad16a597cf30e8b0","tid":540715,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T22:20:22.000Z","msg":"sleeping dog角色 識得將人由水底變到浮上水面"},{"pid":"877e1316673a94a